<h4 id="安装">安装</h4>
<ul>
  <li>
    <p>CocoaPods是用Ruby构建的,可以用macOS上的默认Ruby进行安装</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">sudo gem install cocoapods</code></p>
  </li>
</ul>

